# graphify ignore — gitignore syntax (last match wins, ! negates).
# Defaults already skip node_modules, .next, dist, build, .git, graphify-out,
# and secret-bearing files. Only list what those defaults miss.

# Git worktrees are full duplicate copies of this repo. Indexing one doubles
# every node and invents false "similar to" edges between a file and its own
# copy. The 2026-07-15 run found 398 duplicate files here (45% of the delta).
.claude/worktrees/

# App chrome: favicons, PWA icons, and the silent hero video/poster. No
# knowledge value, and every image costs a separate vision-extraction pass.
**/app/icon.png
**/app/apple-icon.png
**/public/icon-*.png
**/public/videos/hero.mp4
**/public/videos/hero-poster.jpg
